{"tid":1565340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"色按摩師「無懼男友在隔壁」強迫性侵　女大生淚訴：嚇到不敢叫","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:44:19.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3b09ab940791fb42844176d310aa19738cc2531e","tid":1565340,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"一名女大生與男友相約到<span style=\"color: red;\">台北</span>市開封街一處養生館舒壓，2人隔著布簾分開按摩，女子進行到一半時突然遭按摩師強行性侵得逞，事後女子不敢張揚直到隔天隱忍不住才報警。按摩師坦承犯行但辯稱是兩情相悅，且還被查出是逃逸外勞，遭警方依法送辦。<br />\n <br />\n警方調查，慘遭性侵的女大生花花（化名），9日晚上與男友相約到開封街一處養生館按摩，2人隔著一個布簾分開，但男友殊不知女友隔著布簾慘遭31歲的阮姓按摩師性侵得逞，直到隔天花花才向男友表示自己遭辱，緊急報警處理。<br />\n <br />\n警方指出，事後花花到婦幼隊完成報案後，轄區分局也到養生館找到該名阮姓按摩師，阮到案後坦承犯行，但辯稱是兩情相悅下發生關係，但警方訊後仍依照強制性交移送地檢署，事後遭檢察官裁定羈押。<br />\n <br />\n警方事後發現，這名阮姓按摩師根本就是個「逃逸外勞」，從2014年以工廠技工名義申請來台工作，但原本2017年就應該結束工作離台，但卻冒用他人身分繼續在養生館上班，也將通報移民署處理。"},{"pid":"aa6c6a48cf88284b2ff94d69a0786e717d203f64","tid":1565340,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:08:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3f0a3de34a7c192e121221868431bc9a74957ed3","tid":1565340,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"好耐無睇聯賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0208fec45a9f0a0a9ff87060ccfef4c83a9b2add","tid":1565340,"uid":105775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"求潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01a25f77864f3be431a77425ffec7cf55531b4e","tid":1565340,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"SOD<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e697f4a40b5650f67b706b9bd328407149c27481","tid":1565340,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"495f87af3f08b6904dc147c774bcaf246bb77620","tid":1565340,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"終於有新聞睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3825324d8cbcd6781d4cc5f1e99eb95b2ef030","tid":1565340,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YxUaVpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxUaVpQ.jpg&h=d4b38d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支爆應該和誰看</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=mymTsZ